{"id": "chunk_00050", "text": "# FILE: Competency of Xray Tech.doc # CATEGORY: Training & Competency # SIZE: 37888 bytes bjbj 48 Competency of Radiology Dep staff.January 2021 Name: [name] X-ray Specialist No. Parameters of work competency Competent Non-Competent 1. Performing all X-ray radiography investigation. 2. Performing all conventional X-ray investigations. Urinary contrast studies IVP, uretrocystography....etc. Hysterosalpingography. 3. Working in normal and digital X-ray machines. 4. Performing panorama and dental radiography. 5. Performing Mammography 6. Usage of PACS system to transfer images Daily, weekly and monthly checkup of machines of X-ray. 8. Working on portable X-ray Machine 9. Applying all safety parameters from radiation hazards for patient and staff. 10.", "metadata": {"source": "Competency of Xray Tech.doc", "category": "Training & Competency", "owner": "Mohamed Fekri Soliman", "pii_status": "anonymized"}}
{"id": "chunk_00051", "text": "le X-ray Machine 9. Applying all safety parameters from radiation hazards for patient and staff. 10. Handling X-ray machines properly with regular daily checkup and calibration. 11. Applying all precautions for machine safety. 12. Proper patient preparation for X-ray investigation. 13. Cases analysis and daily and monthly reporting of number and type of cases. 14. Proper recording of incidental reports and result regularly. 15. Proper dealing with emergency cases in code blue and code yellow. 16. Proper rapid first aid dealing in case of contrast adverse reaction and recording patient in computer system and incidental report. 17. Proper dealing with patient informing about the way of investigation and submitting consent. 18.", "metadata": {"source": "Competency of Xray Tech.doc", "category": "Training & Competency", "owner": "Mohamed Fekri Soliman", "pii_status": "anonymized"}}
